<h2 id="usage"><a href="#usage">Usage</a></h2>

<section class="prose">
  <p>Field provides semantic HTML patterns for accessible forms:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> for grouping related fields</li>
    <li><code>role="group"</code> with <code>.field</code> class for individual fields</li>
    <li><code>.description</code> class for helper text</li>
    <li><code>.error</code> class with <code>role="alert"</code> for error messages</li>
    <li><code>aria-describedby</code> to associate descriptions and errors with inputs</li>
  </ul>
</section>

