<h2 id="accessibility"><a href="#accessibility">Accessibility</a></h2>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li>Always use <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> elements with <code>for</code> attribute matching input <code>id</code></li>
    <li>Associate helper text and errors using <code>aria-describedby</code> on the input</li>
    <li>Use <code>aria-invalid="true"</code> on inputs with errors</li>
    <li>Use <code>role="alert"</code> on error messages for screen reader announcements</li>
    <li>Group related fields with <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code></li>
    <li>Use <code>role="group"</code> for individual field wrappers</li>
  </ul>
</section>



